WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.298 --> 01:37.648
=Episode 5=

01:38.256 --> 01:41.335
In the matter of Lu Changfu,
I can relieve Your Majesty's worries.

01:41.935 --> 01:44.215
But I have three requests.

01:45.055 --> 01:45.855
First,

01:46.575 --> 01:49.215
while I clear the obstacles
on your path,

01:49.215 --> 01:50.295
please support me

01:50.536 --> 01:52.144
in clearing the name of Heiyun Cavalry,

01:52.256 --> 01:53.656
Prince Ding's household,

01:54.215 --> 01:55.695
and my elder brother.

01:57.376 --> 01:59.176
Back then, General Xiuwen said

01:59.376 --> 02:01.056
he returned
by the late Emperor's decree,

02:01.656 --> 02:02.855
but he couldn't present it.

02:03.256 --> 02:04.175
That's why...

02:05.336 --> 02:07.776
Without that imperial decree,
this case can't be overturned.

02:09.135 --> 02:10.336
When I was imprisoned,

02:10.496 --> 02:11.855
Marquis Muyang told me

02:13.615 --> 02:14.816
he destroyed the decree.

02:15.976 --> 02:17.336
How dare he?

02:17.816 --> 02:19.015
Do you trust me?

02:21.295 --> 02:22.256
I trust you, Xiuyao.

02:25.216 --> 02:27.895
There might be a chance
to root out Marquis Muyang.

02:30.336 --> 02:30.960
Okay.

02:31.336 --> 02:32.295
I grant your request.

02:33.015 --> 02:35.376
If Marquis Muyang remains,
there's no peace for the court.

02:35.615 --> 02:36.415
Second,

02:36.536 --> 02:38.256
I request the authority
for investigation.

02:38.336 --> 02:41.295
I request the access to review
all archived files in the Six Ministries,

02:41.536 --> 02:44.096
and the power to interrogate
anyone involved in any case.

02:44.855 --> 02:46.575
I request the authority to make arrests.

02:46.575 --> 02:48.400
Officials of the fifth rank
or lower involved

02:48.496 --> 02:50.695
can be imprisoned directly
in the Imperial Prison.

02:50.992 --> 02:52.855
Also, the privilege
to submit secret memorials.

02:52.855 --> 02:53.895
So I can send secret news

02:54.015 --> 02:55.056
and intelligence

02:55.056 --> 02:56.776
gathered in the capital straight to you.

02:57.256 --> 02:58.135
Third,

02:59.135 --> 03:00.015
I want one person.

03:02.895 --> 03:03.575
Lady.

03:03.575 --> 03:04.776
It's our osmanthus cakes.

03:04.776 --> 03:05.695
Fluffy and refreshing.

03:05.695 --> 03:07.135
Even the Prefect's lady wants them.

03:07.336 --> 03:08.056
Alright.

03:08.135 --> 03:08.855
Please.

03:09.264 --> 03:10.832
(Qingfeng Mingyue Tower)

03:17.216 --> 03:19.376
If Lu Changfu really makes it to Huaixi,

03:20.695 --> 03:22.496
there's no hope left
for the weaponry case.

03:23.056 --> 03:25.536
Taking Marquis Muyang down
will be more difficult.

03:27.695 --> 03:28.895
The Emperor made it clear.

03:29.855 --> 03:30.735
Lu Changfu

03:31.855 --> 03:33.295
must not leave the capital alive.

03:33.536 --> 03:34.455
Good.

03:35.776 --> 03:36.575
Then kill him.

03:36.816 --> 03:38.415
Poison, sword, fire or water?

03:39.615 --> 03:40.976
Which method do you prefer?

03:41.695 --> 03:43.536
Lu Changfu has committed countless sins.

03:44.295 --> 03:46.216
Though we cannot
deal with him by law at present,

03:46.575 --> 03:47.976
he must die.

03:50.376 --> 03:51.575
Xiuyao, what do you think?

03:55.096 --> 03:56.135
In my opinion,

03:56.936 --> 03:58.015
since he must die,

03:59.175 --> 04:00.936
why not let him die
before the officials,

04:01.656 --> 04:03.216
beneath the open sky?

04:04.096 --> 04:05.295
But Mother...

04:06.295 --> 04:08.175
This is ultimately your world.

04:11.495 --> 04:13.815
Yet Marquis Muyang
has the Eight Evils in his faction,

04:14.216 --> 04:16.615
Zhou Chengxiang, Wen Zhong, and Lv Cheng

04:16.615 --> 04:18.615
are now captured and executed.

04:18.615 --> 04:20.696
That Lu Changfu would be dead soon.

04:20.935 --> 04:23.175
Then, do we still kill the others?

04:23.216 --> 04:26.536
All who have owed a debt of blood
certainly deserve death.

04:26.735 --> 04:28.055
Are you sure?

04:29.255 --> 04:33.175
If we killed Lu Changfu,
Marquis Muyang will surely retaliate.

04:35.472 --> 04:37.536
Considering the state
of Prince Ding's house before,

04:37.536 --> 04:38.776
and my circumstances now,

04:39.855 --> 04:41.216
why fear his retaliation?

04:42.175 --> 04:43.615
Your circumstances now?

04:44.456 --> 04:45.735
You are married,

04:46.255 --> 04:47.735
and have a Princess Consort.

04:52.055 --> 04:52.935
Ye Li.

04:53.295 --> 04:54.696
You're free to go now.

04:58.656 --> 04:59.576
To where?

05:00.136 --> 05:01.096
Anywhere you like.

05:02.136 --> 05:04.255
You married me just to leave Lishan.

05:04.935 --> 05:07.696
Now, we've been married awhile.

05:07.935 --> 05:09.295
I could tell the Empress Dowager

05:10.255 --> 05:11.255
that you and I

05:11.495 --> 05:12.576
cannot get along well

05:13.016 --> 05:14.175
and plead for a divorce.

05:15.016 --> 05:17.855
You could return to the Ye Mansion
or leave the capital.

05:18.456 --> 05:20.976
Go to anywhere you desire.

05:28.935 --> 05:29.815
Why stare at me?

05:31.495 --> 05:33.536
You seem strange today.

05:34.255 --> 05:35.536
Always urge me to leave,

05:36.216 --> 05:37.815
even saying any place will do.

05:39.255 --> 05:40.336
Are you planning rebellion?

05:40.615 --> 05:41.536
Nonsense!

05:45.696 --> 05:46.615
I just mean well.

05:47.415 --> 05:49.815
Then, drink this soup up.

05:50.456 --> 05:52.175
Or I have to rewarm it when it cools.

06:02.495 --> 06:05.935
If you're doing this to repay
my life-saving grace in the desert,

06:07.696 --> 06:09.536
those pastries you gave me
in the prison cart

06:10.336 --> 06:11.495
have repaid it.

06:12.255 --> 06:13.615
After all, without the pastries,

06:14.776 --> 06:16.295
I wouldn't survive the prison life.

06:19.495 --> 06:20.536
You remember me?

06:21.615 --> 06:24.415
You never mentioned it.
I thought you'd forgotten.

06:24.855 --> 06:26.136
On our wedding day,

06:26.295 --> 06:28.576
you said "Nice to meet you."

06:30.255 --> 06:31.615
Wasn't it you who'd forgotten?

06:35.255 --> 06:36.935
When did you remember me?

06:37.776 --> 06:39.375
Did you recognize me right away,

06:39.976 --> 06:41.255
or did it come to you later?

06:45.415 --> 06:46.896
I'm talking to you about the divorce.

06:46.896 --> 06:48.536
What I'm asking is also important.

06:54.855 --> 06:56.536
Since we both want
to ask the other first,

06:57.055 --> 06:58.495
why not let the fate decide?

07:01.935 --> 07:04.336
If the characters "Xide Tongbao"
land facing up,

07:04.776 --> 07:05.696
I'll do it your way

07:06.016 --> 07:07.375
and talk about the divorce.

07:08.935 --> 07:10.415
But if the coin comes down tails,

07:10.456 --> 07:11.576
then you'll do my way.

07:11.855 --> 07:14.615
Let's talk about when you remembered me.

07:26.976 --> 07:27.615
Alright.

07:28.016 --> 07:29.255
Then let's follow the fate.

07:30.055 --> 07:33.136
We'll talk about the past first,
then the divorce.

07:38.536 --> 07:41.096
Tell me, when did you remember me?

08:02.096 --> 08:03.735
Five watches at the Yin hour.

08:03.976 --> 08:05.896
Sleep early, rise early.

08:05.976 --> 08:07.976
Care for your health.

08:09.677 --> 08:15.152
(Lu Mansion)

08:17.616 --> 08:19.920
(Three quarters past the Yin hour
is the court session.)

08:20.136 --> 08:22.735
From Chongren Lane,
via Yanximen Street, to the imperial city.

08:23.696 --> 08:25.096
In such a long route,

08:25.255 --> 08:28.176
no matter how cautious,
one will reveal weak spots.

08:28.176 --> 08:29.576
We could set an ambush ahead.

08:29.655 --> 08:31.456
When he passes, we'll unleash the bolts,

08:31.535 --> 08:33.456
ensuring his death.

08:33.855 --> 08:34.615
Difficult.

08:35.135 --> 08:36.056
Do you know?

08:36.135 --> 08:38.535
Lu Changfu's carriage
is no ordinary carriage.

08:38.855 --> 08:39.936
(It seems mundane,)

08:40.135 --> 08:41.096
(but actually,)

08:41.135 --> 08:43.375
(inside is layers of elm wood
sandwiching fine steel.)

08:43.456 --> 08:46.255
(Furthermore, it's guarded by experts.)

08:46.895 --> 08:48.375
We could take action,

08:48.456 --> 08:49.855
but if that strike fails,

08:50.296 --> 08:52.015
it will only make him vigilant.

08:52.216 --> 08:54.416
It won't be easy to strike again.

09:19.984 --> 09:20.456
(Danque Gate)

09:20.456 --> 09:22.816
(From Daming Palace's Longwei Path
to Danque Gate,)

09:23.255 --> 09:24.735
(officials disarm and enter on foot.)

09:25.056 --> 09:28.296
(Within Imperial Palace,
Lu Changfu cannot bring any guards.)

09:28.775 --> 09:29.895
(Once the court adjourns,)

09:30.015 --> 09:32.456
(it's time for the imperial guards
changing shifts.)

09:33.176 --> 09:35.296
(Besides, the security here is weak.)

09:35.855 --> 09:37.775
Perfect for killing him.

09:38.056 --> 09:38.832
Good.

09:39.096 --> 09:39.895
Then our people

09:40.176 --> 09:41.416
set ambush atop tall buildings.

10:00.456 --> 10:01.296
Lord Lu.

10:01.296 --> 10:02.096
Good.

10:03.015 --> 10:03.696
Good.

10:03.920 --> 10:04.615
Good.

10:04.615 --> 10:05.816
Congrats!

10:05.816 --> 10:07.015
Military Governor Lu.

10:07.855 --> 10:09.255
Congrats, Military Governor Lu!

10:09.255 --> 10:10.456
Congrats...

10:10.655 --> 10:11.255
No.

10:11.255 --> 10:13.416
Military Governor Lu.

10:59.120 --> 11:00.144
(Lu Changfu)

11:28.976 --> 11:30.816
Right. Someone from Ye family came,

11:31.056 --> 11:33.176
asking you to go attend
the reunion banquet

11:33.375 --> 11:34.735
for Madam's birthday next month.

11:40.375 --> 11:41.416
Reunion banquet?

11:46.015 --> 11:46.816
Your Majesty.

11:46.855 --> 11:47.655
Empress Dowager.

11:47.816 --> 11:50.495
Marquis Muyang is unwell,
so absent today.

11:56.696 --> 11:59.495
In capital region, four high ministers
have fallen consecutively.

11:59.735 --> 12:03.096
Jingzhao Prefecture has investigated
tirelessly, but found nothing.

12:03.096 --> 12:03.816
I am

12:04.255 --> 12:05.936
too ashamed to hold this position.

12:06.096 --> 12:08.336
Punish me, Your Majesty.

12:10.015 --> 12:12.296
Magistrate Gongshu, don't say that.

12:12.655 --> 12:14.096
Bandits rise all over.

12:14.535 --> 12:15.895
First, they killed Yuan Fang.

12:16.096 --> 12:17.735
Then, they slew four ministers.

12:17.816 --> 12:19.096
Their ferocity is evident.

12:19.255 --> 12:21.296
Magistrate Gongshu,
how could you prevent it?

12:21.816 --> 12:23.296
I cannot blame you alone.

12:23.535 --> 12:25.855
You've been in charge
of Jingzhao Prefecture for six years,

12:25.936 --> 12:27.816
and righted thirty-six
wrongful convictions.

12:27.936 --> 12:29.936
Both Mother and I
are well aware of this.

12:30.015 --> 12:31.936
Never mention the punishment again.

12:32.336 --> 12:33.456
Mother, what do you think?

12:34.855 --> 12:36.416
You speak truth.

12:39.535 --> 12:42.336
Thank you for your grace and kindness.

12:46.816 --> 12:47.615
Your Majesty.

12:48.336 --> 12:49.096
Empress Dowager.

12:49.296 --> 12:51.735
Huaixi is the key
to control the Jianghuai region.

12:51.895 --> 12:54.336
With Military Governor
Lu Changfu now dead,

12:54.336 --> 12:57.655
I suggest to fill role with talent soon.

12:58.535 --> 13:00.096
Any recommendation?

13:07.056 --> 13:08.336
I have a candidate to recommend.

13:09.255 --> 13:12.135
I believe Gongshu Yang
suits this position.

13:12.535 --> 13:14.696
In Xide's Fifth Year,
chaos broke out in Huaizhou Army.

13:14.696 --> 13:16.826
He was once the Magistrate
of Jingzhao Prefecture,

13:16.826 --> 13:18.336
overseeing the grain shipment there.

13:18.495 --> 13:21.696
He shattered thirteen bands
of water bandits, truly a capable officer.

13:22.416 --> 13:25.015
Minister Gongshu truly
boasts notable achievements.

13:25.655 --> 13:27.456
Moreover, he was elevated by Mother.

13:27.456 --> 13:28.535
He is a man of honor.

13:28.936 --> 13:30.336
Though Huaixi is perilous today,

13:30.696 --> 13:33.615
it precisely requires
a devoted minister like him.

13:34.255 --> 13:35.456
What do you think, Mother?

13:37.296 --> 13:39.096
Makes sense.

13:39.735 --> 13:42.576
Minister Gongshu,
will you accept this appointment?

13:45.576 --> 13:46.375
I

13:46.655 --> 13:47.456
accept.

13:48.255 --> 13:51.056
I'll do whatever you say,
Your Majesties.

13:51.735 --> 13:52.495
Good.

13:53.096 --> 13:53.936
Draft an edict.

13:57.015 --> 13:58.216
- Yes.
- Yes.

13:59.296 --> 14:01.072
Promote Gongshu Yang
from Jingzhao Prefecture

14:01.072 --> 14:02.696
to Honorary Minister of War,

14:02.816 --> 14:05.336
and appoint him
as Military Governor of Huaixi.

14:05.696 --> 14:07.135
Bestow upon him Linfu Golden Armor.

14:07.135 --> 14:08.936
In three days,
he departs to assume office.

14:10.135 --> 14:11.255
Thank you, Your Majesty.

14:13.895 --> 14:14.696
Your Majesty,

14:15.296 --> 14:18.296
as Magistrate Gongshu rises
to become Military Governor of Huaixi,

14:18.456 --> 14:20.416
we need a new Magistrate
of Jingzhao Prefecture.

14:20.735 --> 14:22.655
It also requires a suitable candidate.

14:23.135 --> 14:24.855
You speak well.

14:25.696 --> 14:28.696
I think in these times
of rampant banditry,

14:28.936 --> 14:30.672
the successor must
have military experience

14:30.672 --> 14:32.416
to intimidate such petty villains.

14:34.296 --> 14:36.296
Do you have a recommendation?

14:37.296 --> 14:38.096
Prince Ding,

14:38.456 --> 14:39.535
Mo Xiuyao.

14:49.615 --> 14:52.096
The Mingde Hall today was quite lively.

14:52.655 --> 14:55.376
Murong Shen recommended you
as Magistrate of Jingzhao Prefecture.

14:55.535 --> 14:57.216
Zhang Hengyuan was the first to refute.

14:57.296 --> 14:58.096
He said you...

14:58.696 --> 14:59.615
He said

14:59.936 --> 15:02.096
that you're a cripple
and a condemned sinner,

15:02.216 --> 15:03.456
unfit for such a crucial post.

15:04.416 --> 15:06.375
And other members
of Marquis Muyang's faction

15:06.416 --> 15:08.096
said you've stayed indoors
for many years

15:08.096 --> 15:08.855
and are solitary,

15:08.855 --> 15:09.936
shunning all company,

15:10.615 --> 15:12.576
couldn't manage the affairs
of Jingzhao Prefecture

15:12.615 --> 15:14.735
and secure the peace
throughout the capital well.

15:14.816 --> 15:16.895
No need to state everything
in such detail.

15:16.895 --> 15:19.096
I'm just worried
I might not convey it clearly.

15:19.216 --> 15:20.296
Don't interrupt.

15:20.855 --> 15:22.296
At this critical moment,

15:22.615 --> 15:23.735
guess what happened?

15:25.936 --> 15:26.936
Jin, make a guess.

15:30.495 --> 15:32.456
The Duke Hua stood up

15:32.456 --> 15:33.296
and supported you.

15:35.655 --> 15:36.535
Duke Hua?

15:36.655 --> 15:37.176
Yes.

15:37.176 --> 15:37.976
Duke Hua.

15:38.296 --> 15:40.375
He hadn't spoken at court in years.

15:40.416 --> 15:42.096
But somehow he chose today to speak up.

15:42.135 --> 15:44.936
Murong Shen and Marquis Muyang's faction
were in a constant quarrel,

15:44.936 --> 15:45.936
with no resolution.

15:46.336 --> 15:48.816
But Duke Hua represents
the military might of Dachu.

15:48.936 --> 15:50.096
The moment he spoke,

15:50.096 --> 15:52.056
the tide instantly turned.

15:52.056 --> 15:54.296
He sent the losing faction
stumbling into the city moat,

15:54.895 --> 15:56.176
so they couldn't resist.

15:56.535 --> 15:59.015
Then you were confirmed.

15:59.096 --> 16:00.655
The Empress Dowager said nothing?

16:00.655 --> 16:02.615
Perhaps she deferred to the Duke Hua.

16:03.735 --> 16:04.535
Wrong.

16:05.936 --> 16:09.135
Though the Marquis Muyang once basked
in the Empress Dowager's favor,

16:09.615 --> 16:11.495
he's ancient history now.

16:11.735 --> 16:14.336
The current favorite is Gongshu Yang.

16:14.735 --> 16:15.775
Though the young emperor

16:15.816 --> 16:17.855
handed over Huaixi to him,

16:17.895 --> 16:19.336
the Empress Dowager couldn't object.

16:20.735 --> 16:24.416
The young emperor's open scheme
is truly awe-inspiring!

16:25.816 --> 16:28.416
As the emperor, one must be capable.

16:28.655 --> 16:30.976
As if you attended court yourself today.

16:32.176 --> 16:34.775
Sitting at home,
I can still get the news.

16:35.176 --> 16:36.416
That is my skill.

16:37.015 --> 16:38.015
But we didn't

16:38.495 --> 16:39.576
kill Lu Changfu.

16:39.576 --> 16:40.615
Who did it?

16:41.336 --> 16:42.375
The emperor said anything?

16:42.816 --> 16:44.936
If it was one persecuted by Lu Changfu

16:44.936 --> 16:46.255
and committed no further evils,

16:46.255 --> 16:47.176
he could be pardoned.

16:49.056 --> 16:50.895
Well, this individual
is truly impressive.

16:51.176 --> 16:52.816
If you find him,
perhaps let him join us.

16:53.176 --> 16:53.816
Right.

16:53.855 --> 16:57.295
The capital's new magistrate
is soon to take office.

16:57.656 --> 16:58.696
How do you think?

16:58.735 --> 17:01.696
I think you've been here far too long.

17:02.095 --> 17:02.936
Time to go.

17:06.295 --> 17:07.735
I heard a few days ago,

17:08.055 --> 17:10.055
the Princess Consort
set your study on fire?

17:10.456 --> 17:11.735
The loss must be significant.

17:12.095 --> 17:14.535
What a temper she has!

17:15.936 --> 17:16.815
Feng Zhiyao,

17:18.335 --> 17:20.535
you plant spies in my residence?

17:21.015 --> 17:22.136
You sure have some guts.

17:23.216 --> 17:24.295
I wouldn't dare.

17:38.095 --> 17:39.280
Where's the Princess Consort?

17:40.335 --> 17:43.095
She went out early this morning.

18:02.160 --> 18:05.648
(Tomb of Seven Martyrs of Lishan)

18:14.669 --> 18:18.035
(Former Teachers and Friends of Lishan)

18:30.335 --> 18:32.136
Lu Changfu framed you incited trouble,

18:33.295 --> 18:34.735
and had you all burned alive.

18:34.936 --> 18:36.255
Now that justice has been served.

18:38.216 --> 18:39.216
Rest in peace.

18:46.335 --> 18:47.136
Are you okay?

18:47.936 --> 18:49.416
You ate too much this morning?

18:51.656 --> 18:53.216
I didn't have breakfast at all.

18:53.735 --> 18:55.136
It's the boatman's fault.

18:55.815 --> 18:58.295
The constant swaying
back and forth made me dizzy.

19:01.095 --> 19:02.216
We're leaving soon.

19:02.856 --> 19:04.936
Aren't you going
to say something to them?

19:07.535 --> 19:08.335
No need.

19:09.095 --> 19:10.055
Let's go home.

19:11.295 --> 19:12.735
Enjoy your meal.

19:12.882 --> 19:15.535
(Tea)

19:15.535 --> 19:16.856
What's your plan next?

19:18.735 --> 19:20.216
Grandmother's birthday is next month.

19:20.416 --> 19:21.856
Planning to go back to Ye Mansion.

19:23.856 --> 19:24.735
Time to confront them?

19:25.735 --> 19:27.295
It had to happen someday.

19:29.735 --> 19:31.535
Just be careful in everything.

19:31.656 --> 19:32.896
Earlier in Suixue Pass,

19:33.095 --> 19:34.815
someone snatched Yuan Fang from us.

19:34.936 --> 19:35.735
And now,

19:35.936 --> 19:38.095
someone acted
on the very same day we did,

19:38.095 --> 19:39.856
killing Tian Feng,
Chen Fenyan, and Lu Zhi.

19:40.055 --> 19:42.456
Someone else is targeting
Marquis Muyang behind the scenes.

19:42.696 --> 19:44.295
Perhaps we're being watched too.

19:45.136 --> 19:46.295
I'll be careful.

19:48.936 --> 19:52.136
Still found nothing
about those people at the Suixue Pass.

19:52.735 --> 19:55.896
They retreat and advance with discipline,
and are quite strong fighters.

19:56.616 --> 20:00.095
If we can identify them,
round them all up.

20:00.616 --> 20:02.055
But without any leads,

20:02.696 --> 20:04.735
they aren't our top priority.

20:05.735 --> 20:08.896
For now, they are not our enemies.

20:09.255 --> 20:11.055
Let them be
as long as they don't hinder us.

20:11.456 --> 20:12.255
Do you think

20:13.095 --> 20:15.295
those who killed
Tian Feng and the other two

20:15.696 --> 20:18.216
could be the same group
we encountered at the Suixue Pass?

20:18.936 --> 20:21.535
Are they all working
for the young emperor?

20:22.856 --> 20:24.815
Not really.

20:25.936 --> 20:28.216
Who else then?

20:28.696 --> 20:31.495
Can't be the Empress Dowager's faction
fighting among themselves.

20:32.656 --> 20:33.896
In the court today,

20:34.800 --> 20:36.876
besides the Emperor
and the Empress Dowager's forces,

20:36.876 --> 20:39.255
it must be the influence
of Duke Hua's faction.

20:39.535 --> 20:42.495
Tian Feng and his men
served Marquis Muyang.

20:42.815 --> 20:44.095
Now they're dead.

20:44.535 --> 20:47.095
Whoever benefits most from this

20:47.335 --> 20:50.055
was the mastermind behind this matter.

20:51.495 --> 20:52.295
Makes sense.

20:53.255 --> 20:54.055
Right.

20:54.335 --> 20:56.335
I found a new place
to settle in the capital.

20:56.815 --> 20:59.696
No need to send messages
to the Ye Mansion if you want me.

20:59.856 --> 21:01.136
You're leaving the Ye Mansion?

21:02.136 --> 21:04.015
Aren't you the head of their security?

21:04.856 --> 21:06.456
Head of security is nothing special.

21:06.735 --> 21:08.255
The beds at Ye Mansion are too hard.

21:08.255 --> 21:09.136
The bedding is damp.

21:09.495 --> 21:11.055
And food is bland every day.

21:11.095 --> 21:12.416
Because of you,

21:12.416 --> 21:13.896
I infiltrated into the Ye Mansion.

21:13.936 --> 21:16.216
Three years through heat and cold
was really hard work.

21:17.015 --> 21:18.095
Now that business is done,

21:18.535 --> 21:20.815
time for me to find
somewhere else to settle.

21:22.535 --> 21:24.335
So where's the new place?

21:30.136 --> 21:31.376
Xiangqi Pavilion.

21:33.416 --> 21:34.495
Xiangqi Pavilion?

21:35.936 --> 21:38.015
Master Guan would tan your hide
if he knew it.

21:38.735 --> 21:41.535
He was wilder than me
back when he was young.

21:42.176 --> 21:42.976
Really?

21:45.136 --> 21:45.936
Qingshuang,

21:46.295 --> 21:47.896
is Master Guan really that sort?

21:49.535 --> 21:50.616
I don't know.

21:53.255 --> 21:54.055
Qingshuang

21:54.255 --> 21:55.136
is here too?

21:56.015 --> 21:56.815
Of course.

22:01.896 --> 22:02.696
Li.

22:03.335 --> 22:06.335
Have you been settling in alright
at Prince Ding's Mansion?

22:07.976 --> 22:09.015
I've been fine.

22:10.055 --> 22:12.176
What about Qingshuang?

22:12.376 --> 22:13.495
Has she gotten used to it?

22:14.856 --> 22:16.295
Why couldn't she?

22:17.815 --> 22:18.616
Senior brother.

22:19.015 --> 22:22.335
What you should be worrying about
isn't Qingshuang, but yourself.

22:23.495 --> 22:24.696
Now Lu Changfu is dead.

22:25.055 --> 22:27.696
He was burned alive inside the palace.

22:27.936 --> 22:29.656
That'd definitely attract scrutiny.

22:31.136 --> 22:33.696
Living in such a flaunting place
like Xiangqi Pavilion,

22:33.815 --> 22:35.335
you should be extra careful.

22:35.696 --> 22:36.936
I know it.

22:37.216 --> 22:39.295
You also need to be careful.

22:39.815 --> 22:42.696
That Prince Ding isn't one
to underestimate.

22:43.936 --> 22:46.456
Rest easy. We're getting along fine.

22:47.216 --> 22:48.015
Really?

22:48.575 --> 22:49.376
Really.

22:49.904 --> 22:50.856
Before leaving Lishan,

22:50.856 --> 22:52.936
I asked Senior He to divine my fortune.

22:53.255 --> 22:54.495
He said that Prince Ding and I

22:54.575 --> 22:55.976
will get along well

22:55.976 --> 22:56.936
and have many heirs.

22:57.095 --> 22:57.856
Well then,

22:59.456 --> 23:00.856
how's Senior He?

23:01.696 --> 23:02.656
He's been fine,

23:03.696 --> 23:06.095
but always worrying about
the tree in front of his house.

23:07.255 --> 23:08.775
He told me many times

23:08.856 --> 23:10.055
to help him

23:10.095 --> 23:12.696
cut that tree down during this trip.

23:19.616 --> 23:20.416
Let's go.

23:20.856 --> 23:21.535
Excuse me,

23:22.000 --> 23:22.864
check.

23:32.176 --> 23:32.775
Your Highness.

23:36.616 --> 23:37.775
What's the noise outside?

23:38.176 --> 23:38.856
Who's here?

23:39.896 --> 23:41.136
It's His Highness's friend.

23:41.136 --> 23:42.096
In the front courtyard.

23:42.976 --> 23:43.775
A friend?

23:44.896 --> 23:45.616
Ding says

23:45.616 --> 23:48.015
it's Feng Zhiyao
from Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

23:48.015 --> 23:49.216
He's here to borrow a horse.

23:50.775 --> 23:51.656
I'll go check.

23:52.535 --> 23:53.295
Your Highness.

23:53.295 --> 23:55.896
Shouldn't you freshen up a bit
before meeting guests?

23:58.575 --> 23:59.295
Alright.

23:59.295 --> 24:00.216
But do hurry.

24:14.255 --> 24:16.055
Jingfan isn't spirited enough.

24:16.856 --> 24:17.815
I want your Lieyun.

24:18.335 --> 24:19.456
You can't manage Lieyun.

24:20.535 --> 24:21.495
Ridiculous!

24:21.656 --> 24:23.015
If you can, why wouldn't I?

24:23.136 --> 24:24.856
Jingfan is Lieyun's colt.

24:24.896 --> 24:25.936
I won't ride the son.

24:25.936 --> 24:26.936
I want its father.

24:29.335 --> 24:30.136
Master Feng.

24:30.456 --> 24:32.936
Lieyun was raised
on desert wind and sand.

24:33.015 --> 24:34.136
It recognizes its master.

24:34.176 --> 24:36.456
Last year, it bit
a Hu merchant's arm in West Market.

24:36.495 --> 24:38.255
Be careful not to get hurt.

24:39.735 --> 24:42.136
Tomorrow's the polo match.
I need a fine steed.

24:42.136 --> 24:43.136
Don't be stingy.

24:53.616 --> 24:55.696
Back then, it fought through
three towns in Cangbei.

24:55.696 --> 24:57.055
Tomorrow, I'll ride it

24:57.136 --> 24:59.295
and score three consecutive goals
on the polo field.

25:07.575 --> 25:08.495
Mo Lao'er.

25:08.936 --> 25:09.575
Help me!

25:09.575 --> 25:10.376
Help me!

25:13.295 --> 25:14.735
Don't just watch me there!

25:16.295 --> 25:18.295
Get out of the way!

25:42.616 --> 25:43.255
Are you alright?

25:45.176 --> 25:45.976
I'm fine.

25:46.136 --> 25:46.936
Good.

25:48.208 --> 25:48.815
Let's go.

25:53.535 --> 25:54.896
I'm not fine.

25:59.886 --> 26:01.702
(Day and Night Diligence)

26:01.896 --> 26:02.696
You know what?

26:03.216 --> 26:05.856
The Princess Consort
suits you rather well.

26:09.616 --> 26:10.216
Let me use it.

26:10.976 --> 26:12.976
I'll go meet your Princess Consort.

26:21.735 --> 26:24.495
It's nothing, just a scratch.

26:25.136 --> 26:27.735
How can it be nothing?
Look, it's bleeding.

26:28.696 --> 26:30.616
You told me to meet guests
after freshening up.

26:31.376 --> 26:32.535
I didn't expect

26:32.535 --> 26:34.456
Master Feng's horsemanship
to be so mediocre.

26:34.456 --> 26:35.976
He dared to ride His Highness's horse?

26:36.015 --> 26:37.335
Overestimating himself.

26:40.376 --> 26:42.575
I am Feng Zhiyao
from Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

26:43.095 --> 26:44.136
Pleased to meet you.

26:47.095 --> 26:49.255
You got injured today because of me.

26:50.416 --> 26:53.535
I felt quite guilty about it,
so I brought ointment for you.

26:57.416 --> 26:59.216
You were gossiping about me
behind my back?

27:03.015 --> 27:05.535
Someone like him
won't hold it against you.

27:05.896 --> 27:07.456
Apologize to Master Feng.

27:08.735 --> 27:10.216
- Pardon my offense.
- It's alright.

27:10.936 --> 27:12.295
Just joking.

27:13.095 --> 27:13.775
Please.

27:13.775 --> 27:14.495
Thank you.

27:16.095 --> 27:17.255
This Ice Toad Ointment

27:17.696 --> 27:19.416
is excellent for healing wounds.

27:19.760 --> 27:21.696
I'll gift you
a set of twelve colors rouge

27:21.696 --> 27:23.015
as a compensation tomorrow.

27:23.416 --> 27:24.495
I'll take the ointment,

27:25.335 --> 27:27.495
but not the rouge. I don't need it.

27:29.616 --> 27:30.416
Fine.

27:30.815 --> 27:32.535
Since you accept this ointment,

27:32.656 --> 27:34.136
I'll assume you accepted my apology.

27:34.456 --> 27:36.255
Rouge isn't essential, anyway.

27:37.335 --> 27:38.696
However,

27:38.696 --> 27:40.335
I could give you a formula.

27:41.656 --> 27:42.575
What kind of formula?

27:43.616 --> 27:46.015
A secret formula to cure
His Highness's peculiar temper.

27:47.495 --> 27:48.575
Please tell.

27:50.896 --> 27:52.295
His Highness

27:52.616 --> 27:54.815
has gotten used
to being alone over the years.

27:54.815 --> 27:58.095
He needs a beautiful wife like you.

27:58.656 --> 27:59.575
In my opinion,

28:00.136 --> 28:01.656
let him spend less time indoors

28:01.744 --> 28:03.216
and take him out more to experience

28:03.216 --> 28:04.976
the hustle and bustle of ordinary life.

28:05.376 --> 28:07.015
Then his peculiar temper will fade away.

28:07.575 --> 28:09.575
His Highness
is such a well-behaved person.

28:09.896 --> 28:12.255
Master Feng, don't lead him astray.

28:13.775 --> 28:15.535
He doesn't need my lead.

28:17.456 --> 28:21.255
His Highness is as cunning
as a squid, full of schemes.

28:25.176 --> 28:25.936
See?

28:27.095 --> 28:28.976
Next time you gossip
behind someone's back,

28:29.055 --> 28:30.136
keep your voice down.

28:35.575 --> 28:36.095
Farewell.

28:45.176 --> 28:53.696
♪Huainan rice fills tribute boats♪

28:54.295 --> 29:02.416
♪Longyou grapes inebriate royal towers♪

29:03.696 --> 29:12.176
♪A hundred performances are staged
on the Linde Hall♪

29:12.575 --> 29:13.656
Sigh over a hundred years?

29:14.815 --> 29:17.976
These lyrics likely originate
from Lishan, don't they?

29:19.136 --> 29:20.015
Lishan?

29:45.095 --> 29:46.775
It has been many years

29:47.416 --> 29:48.775
since I met old acquaintances.

29:49.976 --> 29:52.976
Are you thinking of Wanzhou?

29:55.176 --> 29:58.575
Back then, we had no choice.

29:59.095 --> 30:00.495
It was good for Wanzhou

30:00.936 --> 30:02.735
to stay at Lishan.

30:05.136 --> 30:06.960
How are things at Prince Ding's Mansion?

30:07.376 --> 30:09.495
They've been married for some time now.

30:10.976 --> 30:11.775
Your Majesty,

30:12.416 --> 30:14.656
the Princess Consort
has been relatively idle lately.

30:15.216 --> 30:16.376
Ms. Wen

30:16.376 --> 30:18.095
has been living a reclusive life.

30:18.456 --> 30:19.335
I heard

30:19.575 --> 30:23.015
she refused to see the Princess Consort
the first day after the wedding.

30:27.495 --> 30:28.696
Would you like to meet her?

30:35.088 --> 30:37.525
(Shende Shop)

30:49.376 --> 30:50.896
We've suffered a significant loss.

30:52.176 --> 30:53.775
Sorry for that.

30:53.775 --> 30:56.696
In recent years, the common people
have mostly practiced frugality.

30:56.696 --> 30:59.856
The porcelain market
in the capital is indeed depressed.

31:00.176 --> 31:01.775
My luck hasn't been good either.

31:01.856 --> 31:02.656
Some days ago,

31:02.656 --> 31:03.735
a boatload of fabrics

31:03.735 --> 31:04.856
to Yangzhou got ruined.

31:05.176 --> 31:07.335
The boat capsized,
and the fabrics were all lost.

31:07.335 --> 31:08.176
Indeed.

31:08.376 --> 31:09.696
I'm having my unlucky year.

31:10.376 --> 31:11.295
Your Highness,

31:11.495 --> 31:14.656
my shop is located in
the most remote corner of East Market.

31:14.656 --> 31:16.696
It rarely sees customers on normal days.

31:16.896 --> 31:19.255
Plus, much of the stored grain
has spoiled,

31:19.856 --> 31:20.575
hence the losses.

31:21.535 --> 31:23.535
The antique shop business is tough.

31:23.535 --> 31:24.376
Your Highness.

31:24.976 --> 31:26.896
I feel deeply ashamed.

31:27.216 --> 31:29.896
I hope to resign from this position.

31:29.896 --> 31:31.055
Yes, Your Highness.

31:31.376 --> 31:32.656
We aren't

31:33.095 --> 31:35.095
cut out for this steward position.

31:35.095 --> 31:37.456
I think you should handle it yourself.

31:37.456 --> 31:39.095
You hail from Lishan,

31:39.095 --> 31:40.656
full of learning and wisdom.

31:40.656 --> 31:44.376
Surely you have the means
to manage the shops properly,

31:44.376 --> 31:45.775
turning losses into profits.

31:45.775 --> 31:46.976
Yes.

31:47.535 --> 31:50.216
After quitting your jobs,
where do you all intend to go?

31:51.055 --> 31:52.696
My son is about to take the civil exams.

31:53.216 --> 31:54.335
I must go be with him.

31:55.295 --> 31:56.735
My parents are getting on in years,

31:56.815 --> 31:58.216
so I must go be with them.

31:58.896 --> 32:00.535
I've been worn out lately,

32:00.535 --> 32:01.735
and want to travel around

32:01.896 --> 32:02.735
to unwind.

32:03.055 --> 32:03.856
Right.

32:04.176 --> 32:06.136
I've been in the capital
for several years.

32:06.136 --> 32:07.055
And now,

32:07.176 --> 32:08.535
I found my loved one.

32:08.735 --> 32:09.856
I plan to get married.

32:12.055 --> 32:14.255
You even found love
in managing the shop?

32:14.856 --> 32:16.055
It shows this shop

32:16.055 --> 32:17.656
has quite auspicious Feng Shui.

32:18.976 --> 32:19.775
I see.

32:20.335 --> 32:21.696
Running a business is challenging.

32:21.976 --> 32:24.136
These past years, you have worked hard.

32:24.575 --> 32:25.376
Not at all.

32:25.376 --> 32:26.976
Grandfather once taught me

32:26.976 --> 32:28.735
to treat meritorious people well.

32:28.976 --> 32:29.976
I will remember

32:30.055 --> 32:31.335
your loyalty and dedication.

32:31.535 --> 32:32.896
You flatter me.

32:34.456 --> 32:35.416
Before I leave,

32:35.735 --> 32:37.176
Master Zhu entrusted me with

32:37.176 --> 32:39.815
this recommendation letter
for Steward Yang's son.

32:40.616 --> 32:43.856
He asked me to deliver it to Lord Zhou,
who oversees this year's civil exams.

32:44.055 --> 32:46.535
Your son is Master Zhu's last disciple.

32:46.616 --> 32:48.735
I bet Lord Zhou would look after him.

32:51.976 --> 32:52.856
Impossible!

32:53.015 --> 32:54.775
How could my son
be Master Zhu's disciple?

32:54.936 --> 32:56.095
Back in Yangzhou,

32:56.176 --> 32:59.815
you curried favor with a fellow villager
of Master Zhu to secure admission.

32:59.976 --> 33:01.815
Master Zhu is a literary authority.

33:01.856 --> 33:04.295
Would he lie just
to claim a relationship with you?

33:04.896 --> 33:05.656
Mind your words.

33:05.656 --> 33:07.335
Lishan's current status is uncertain.

33:07.335 --> 33:09.656
You are jeopardizing
my son's career path.

33:11.575 --> 33:13.376
You should be the one
to mind your words.

33:14.376 --> 33:16.495
Lishan has sealed its gate
just to compile texts.

33:16.616 --> 33:18.136
The palace guards have been stationed

33:18.376 --> 33:20.136
to keep the tranquility of the mountain.

33:20.136 --> 33:23.255
You rashly presume imperial intentions,
trying to condemn Lishan.

33:23.376 --> 33:24.735
This is a grave offense.

33:28.775 --> 33:29.656
Steward Wang.

33:30.575 --> 33:33.176
Over these years, those
on the mountain have lacked food.

33:33.176 --> 33:35.616
Thank you for frequently
sending rice and provisions there.

33:35.616 --> 33:36.616
N-Not me.

33:37.856 --> 33:39.416
I never did that.

33:39.416 --> 33:40.376
Lishan Mountain

33:40.376 --> 33:41.896
is heavily guarded.

33:41.896 --> 33:43.335
How could I possibly send anything?

33:43.616 --> 33:44.176
Your Highness.

33:44.176 --> 33:45.095
Don't slander me.

33:45.095 --> 33:47.136
This could cost me my life!

33:47.136 --> 33:50.335
The teachers on the mountain
can all attest to this.

33:50.856 --> 33:53.055
Wait, impossible!

33:53.055 --> 33:54.936
Impossible!

33:55.495 --> 33:56.136
Impossible!

33:56.815 --> 33:57.775
Steward Zhou.

33:58.335 --> 33:59.216
What do you think?

34:07.184 --> 34:07.976
Your Highness,

34:08.215 --> 34:10.376
I might've took the wrong ledger.

34:10.376 --> 34:11.575
I'll review accounts again

34:11.575 --> 34:13.135
and get you a detailed ledger.

34:13.376 --> 34:14.376
You must account

34:14.376 --> 34:15.575
for everything carefully.

34:15.695 --> 34:16.495
Otherwise,

34:16.856 --> 34:18.336
he'll break your legs.

34:18.376 --> 34:19.816
Yes.

34:20.095 --> 34:20.656
Yes.

34:23.376 --> 34:24.135
How about you guys?

34:24.856 --> 34:25.655
Yes.

34:25.776 --> 34:27.776
Perhaps we made a mistake.

34:27.776 --> 34:29.095
We'll go back and check.

34:29.256 --> 34:30.456
- Right!
- Right!

34:31.095 --> 34:31.695
Let's go.

34:32.296 --> 34:33.055
Well...

34:33.575 --> 34:34.256
Hurry.

34:34.336 --> 34:35.135
Let's go.

34:36.135 --> 34:37.376
I told you we shouldn't do so.

34:37.376 --> 34:38.128
Exactly.

34:41.135 --> 34:41.976
Your Highness.

34:42.055 --> 34:43.495
We have no steward now.

34:44.816 --> 34:46.135
I have a candidate in mind.

34:47.416 --> 34:48.175
Wei Zhuang.

34:50.095 --> 34:50.816
Zhuang.

34:50.816 --> 34:52.135
- Aunt Wang.
- Wonderful news!

34:52.135 --> 34:53.655
Someone sent you a job offer,

34:53.655 --> 34:55.256
asking you to be steward.

34:55.456 --> 34:56.256
A job offer?

34:56.695 --> 34:57.695
Which shop?

34:57.695 --> 34:58.976
Shende Shop.

34:59.175 --> 35:00.575
I heard from my husband

35:00.575 --> 35:01.615
that the items there

35:01.615 --> 35:03.416
are all worth a fortune.

35:03.416 --> 35:06.456
Just a water cup this big alone
can fetch fifty string.

35:07.296 --> 35:09.376
If Wei Zhuang can secure
this steward position,

35:09.695 --> 35:12.215
your family's hardships
would finally be over.

35:14.764 --> 35:16.208
(Employment Contract
for Shende Shop Steward)

35:22.653 --> 35:23.888
(Shende Shop)

35:31.376 --> 35:32.495
You need a steward?

35:34.256 --> 35:35.055
Yes.

36:00.296 --> 36:01.095
Your Highness,

36:01.296 --> 36:02.615
want to eat something?

36:05.976 --> 36:09.336
Even for composing a new piece,
you shouldn't play for days without rest.

36:09.736 --> 36:11.336
How can your body handle this?

36:17.416 --> 36:17.976
Your Highness.

36:21.655 --> 36:22.816
An imperial decree

36:23.135 --> 36:25.296
requires you and His Highness
to enter tomorrow.

36:26.615 --> 36:27.456
His Highness and I?

36:28.535 --> 36:29.055
Yes.

36:30.695 --> 36:33.535
Along with Prince Ding
and Princess Ding.

37:32.896 --> 37:34.175
You're still up?

37:43.655 --> 37:45.416
We're about to enter
the palace tomorrow.

37:46.256 --> 37:47.655
Yet you can sleep soundly?

37:52.376 --> 37:54.416
We'll go meet
the Empress Dowager tomorrow,

37:54.768 --> 37:56.456
so I should rest early,

37:58.256 --> 37:59.736
regulate my breath

38:00.015 --> 38:01.615
and perform well tomorrow.

38:09.256 --> 38:11.695
I didn't expect
you would be so carefree.

38:15.856 --> 38:17.256
Should I be nervous?

38:18.695 --> 38:20.856
Lishan Academy has been
neglected for eight years.

38:21.695 --> 38:23.575
The Empress Dowager
suddenly summons you.

38:24.175 --> 38:26.015
Shouldn't you be nervous?

38:26.456 --> 38:28.256
Lishan Academy has been closed for years

38:28.695 --> 38:30.416
without receiving the emperor's summons,

38:30.695 --> 38:32.535
because it's been
compiling texts these years.

38:33.095 --> 38:33.936
But I think

38:34.256 --> 38:37.495
the Empress Dowager has never forgotten
the teachers on Lishan Mountain,

38:38.135 --> 38:41.135
Otherwise, she wouldn't dispatch guards
to protect Lishan's tranquility.

38:41.575 --> 38:43.095
Do you truly think so?

38:44.816 --> 38:46.856
I have admired the Empress Dowager
since childhood

38:47.456 --> 38:49.615
and often met the Empress Dowager
with my mom.

38:49.904 --> 38:51.376
The Empress Dowager bestowed upon me

38:51.376 --> 38:53.976
palace-exclusive Jiuchong cakes
and Guifei fruits.

38:54.336 --> 38:56.135
She has shown kindness
to my mom and me.

38:56.575 --> 38:59.416
So, I have nothing to nervous about.

39:16.055 --> 39:16.936
In that case,

39:18.376 --> 39:19.655
rest early.

39:41.015 --> 39:41.736
Your Highness.

39:41.896 --> 39:42.816
Take it easy.

39:45.215 --> 39:45.776
Your Highness.

39:46.976 --> 39:49.135
I didn't sleep well last night
and woke up late.

39:49.575 --> 39:50.095
Sorry.

39:52.296 --> 39:52.816
Let's go.

40:06.936 --> 40:07.456
Let me do it.

40:09.336 --> 40:10.095
Your Highness.

40:10.095 --> 40:11.336
Let me handle this menial task.

40:12.416 --> 40:13.040
It's nothing.

40:40.416 --> 40:41.008
Let's go.

40:42.288 --> 40:43.015
So heavy.

40:43.216 --> 40:46.352
(Pastry)

41:11.776 --> 41:13.175
Li, slow down.

41:13.736 --> 41:14.575
Your Majesty.

41:14.695 --> 41:15.456
Li.

41:15.456 --> 41:17.135
Your Majesty, I've missed you so much.

41:18.095 --> 41:18.896
You've grown taller.

41:22.615 --> 41:23.736
Wanzhou.

41:23.736 --> 41:24.816
Mom.

41:35.575 --> 41:36.816
It's been years.

41:37.336 --> 41:39.615
Have you settled back
into life in the capital?

41:40.215 --> 41:41.215
Very well.

41:41.695 --> 41:42.776
Thank you, Your Majesty.

41:43.175 --> 41:46.055
Your maternal grandfather, Headmaster Xu,
was once my teacher too.

41:46.856 --> 41:48.655
How has he been?

41:48.655 --> 41:49.896
And how are the other teachers?

41:50.976 --> 41:51.816
Your Majesty,

41:52.055 --> 41:52.976
they're all well.

41:53.936 --> 41:56.456
Grandfather is in good health,
busy compiling texts.

41:56.776 --> 42:00.015
Knowing I was coming down the mountain,
he asked me to convey his regards to you.

42:00.615 --> 42:01.976
The other teachers are well too.

42:02.615 --> 42:04.135
They teach lessons

42:04.376 --> 42:05.896
and assign coursework diligently.

42:06.615 --> 42:08.736
What lessons are taught there now?

42:09.816 --> 42:11.095
Astronomy, calendrics,

42:11.095 --> 42:12.256
I Ching and numerology.

42:12.256 --> 42:13.135
All are included.

42:13.856 --> 42:16.055
Grandfather also instructs scholars

42:16.055 --> 42:17.575
to stay informed on current affairs.

42:18.575 --> 42:19.376
Really?

42:19.976 --> 42:21.256
How does he teach these?

42:21.655 --> 42:22.945
While proofing and annotating

42:22.945 --> 42:25.135
the Treatise on Rivers and Waterways,

42:25.936 --> 42:27.575
he often mentioned your remarkable feat

42:27.575 --> 42:29.520
of changing the canal transport method
back then.

42:29.776 --> 42:31.015
Knowing after the rerouting,

42:31.015 --> 42:32.936
thirty-thousand fewer trackers
were conscripted,

42:32.936 --> 42:34.575
and taxes were reduced by forty percent,

42:34.816 --> 42:37.936
the teachers all say you demonstrate
extraordinary governance talent,

42:37.936 --> 42:38.816
and deeply admire you.

42:43.088 --> 42:45.490
(Preview)

42:45.816 --> 42:46.615
Your Highness.

42:47.015 --> 42:48.776
Is Her Highness planning

42:48.776 --> 42:49.456
to steal a tree?

42:49.615 --> 42:50.336
Who's there?

42:50.336 --> 42:51.336
Tree thief!

42:51.336 --> 42:52.215
Stop!

42:53.695 --> 42:54.535
Why cut a tree?

42:54.976 --> 42:56.376
Could we talk inside?

42:56.495 --> 42:57.856
Now you're embarrassed?

42:58.095 --> 42:59.615
There's plenty of mud on your shoes.

43:00.095 --> 43:00.896
What?

43:01.695 --> 43:03.344
The trip from the Mansion to Shende Shop

43:03.575 --> 43:04.495
is that challenging?

43:06.376 --> 43:07.936
I went to help Wuyou fight.

43:15.257 --> 43:21.849
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.433 --> 43:31.577
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.785 --> 43:37.017
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.241 --> 43:43.257
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.577 --> 43:47.001
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.065 --> 43:53.625
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.681 --> 43:58.617
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.617 --> 44:04.313
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.825 --> 44:13.433
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.329 --> 44:19.833
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.833 --> 44:25.337
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.401 --> 44:29.465
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.753 --> 44:34.977
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.577 --> 44:39.289
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.321 --> 44:44.985
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.753 --> 44:53.721
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.129 --> 45:00.377
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.633 --> 45:06.537
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.537 --> 45:10.657
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.873 --> 45:15.609
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.825 --> 45:21.097
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.337 --> 45:26.777
♪Unbound by form♪
